SELECT ca.sl_candidatepk, ca.lastname, ca.firstname, com.name AS company, ocu.label AS occupation, ind.label AS industry, levenshtein("abe", LOWER(ca.lastname)) AS lastname_lev, levenshtein("chikako", LOWER(ca.firstname)) AS firstname_lev , 100-(levenshtein("abechikako", LOWER(CONCAT(ca.lastname, ca.firstname)))*100/LENGTH(CONCAT(ca.lastname, ca.firstname))) AS ratio  FROM sl_candidate AS ca  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile AS cap ON (cap.candidatefk = ca.sl_candidatepk) LEFT JOIN sl_occupation AS ocu ON (ocu.sl_occupationpk = cap.occupationfk) LEFT JOIN sl_industry AS ind ON (ind.sl_industrypk = cap.industryfk) LEFT JOIN sl_company AS com ON (com.sl_companypk = cap.companyfk) LEFT JOIN sl_contact AS cont ON (cont.itemfk = ca.sl_candidatepk) WHERE  ( (ca.lastname LIKE "abe%" AND levenshtein("chikako", LOWER(ca.firstname)) < 3)  OR (ca.lastname LIKE "%abe" AND levenshtein("chikako", LOWER(ca.firstname)) < 3) ) ORDER BY ratio DESC, lastname_lev ASC, ca.firstname ASC LIMIT 100 OFFSET 0

SELECT scpr.*, scrs.*, scan.*,
        scan.date_created as date_added,
        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,
        slog.loginpk as creatorfk, CONCAT(slog.firstname, " ", slog.lastname) as creator, slog.pseudo as creator_short,
        sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
        scom.name as company_name, scom.is_client as cp_client, scom.sl_companypk, scom.sl_companypk as companyfk,
        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,
        IF(sind2.label IS NOT NULL, sind2.label, IF(socc2.label IS NOT NULL, socc2.label,  satt.attributefk)) as attribute_label

SELECT scpr.*, scrs.*, scan.*,
        scan.date_created as date_added,
        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,
        slog.loginpk as creatorfk, CONCAT(slog.firstname, " ", slog.lastname) as creator, slog.pseudo as creator_short,
        sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
        scom.name as company_name, scom.is_client as cp_client, scom.sl_companypk, scom.sl_companypk as companyfk,
        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,
        IF(sind2.label IS NOT NULL, sind2.label, IF(socc2.label IS NOT NULL, socc2.label,  satt.attributefk)) as attribute_label
         FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_attribute as satt ON ((satt.`type` IN ("candi_lang","candi_indus","candi_occu") AND itemfk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_language as slan ON ((slan.sl_languagepk = scan.languagefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_location as sloc ON ((sloc.sl_locationpk = scan.locationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_nationality as snat ON ((snat.sl_nationalitypk = scan.nationalityfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_indus" AND sind2.sl_industrypk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_occu" AND socc2.sl_occupationpk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON ((slog.loginpk = scan.created_by))  LEFT JOIN sl_company_rss as scrs ON ((scrs.companyfk = scom.sl_companypk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  WHERE 1  AND scan.sl_candidatepk = 2598 AND COALESCE(sind.sl_industrypk, 0) <> 126

          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,

          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk)))  WHERE 1  AND ( scan.lastname LIKE "%rika%" OR  scan.firstname LIKE "%rika%" )   AND  scom.name LIKE "%prudential%"   AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY  IF(MAX(ratio) >= MAX(ratio_rev), ratio, ratio_rev) DESC , lastname desc, firstname desc, PK desc  LIMIT  0 ,25

          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-02 11:32:26") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin , scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-02 11:33:00") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "%IFS%" )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY scpr.grade desc  LIMIT  0 ,25

SELECT scpr.*, scrs.*, scan.*,
        scan.date_created as date_added,
        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,
        slog.loginpk as creatorfk, CONCAT(slog.firstname, " ", slog.lastname) as creator, slog.pseudo as creator_short,
        sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
        scom.name as company_name, scom.is_client as cp_client, scom.sl_companypk, scom.sl_companypk as companyfk,
        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,
        IF(sind2.label IS NOT NULL, sind2.label, IF(socc2.label IS NOT NULL, socc2.label,  satt.attributefk)) as attribute_label
         FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_attribute as satt ON ((satt.`type` IN ("candi_lang","candi_indus","candi_occu") AND itemfk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_language as slan ON ((slan.sl_languagepk = scan.languagefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_location as sloc ON ((sloc.sl_locationpk = scan.locationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_nationality as snat ON ((snat.sl_nationalitypk = scan.nationalityfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_indus" AND sind2.sl_industrypk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_occu" AND socc2.sl_occupationpk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON ((slog.loginpk = scan.created_by))  LEFT JOIN sl_company_rss as scrs ON ((scrs.companyfk = scom.sl_companypk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  WHERE 1  AND scan.sl_candidatepk = 420569
6sec - start: 2017-02-02 11:45:04 / end: 2017-02-02 11:45:10
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

               IFNULL(TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, slc.date_birth, '2017-02-02 11:45:10'), '-') AS age
               FROM sl_candidate slc
               LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile slcp on slcp.candidatefk = slc.sl_candidatepk
               LEFT JOIN sl_company sc on sc.sl_companypk = slcp.companyfk
               WHERE slc.sl_candidatepk = '345309'

          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,

          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-06 14:29:47") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin , scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-06 14:30:48") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "%digital strategy%"  and scan.locationfk  IN  (1) )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY full_salary asc  LIMIT  0 ,25

SELECT  levenshtein("ko", TRIM(LOWER(scan.lastname))) AS lastname_lev ,  levenshtein("ko", TRIM(LOWER(scan.firstname))) AS firstname_lev ,  100-(levenshtein("ko", LOWER(scan.lastname))*100/LENGTH(scan.lastname)) AS ratio ,  100-(levenshtein("ko", LOWER(scan.firstname))*100/LENGTH(scan.firstname)) AS ratio_rev , scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-06 16:36:39") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk)))  WHERE 1  AND ( scan.lastname LIKE "%ko%" OR  scan.firstname LIKE "%ko%" )   AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY  IF(MAX(ratio) >= MAX(ratio_rev), ratio, ratio_rev) DESC , lastname desc, firstname desc, PK desc  LIMIT  0 ,25

SELECT ca.sl_candidatepk, ca.lastname, ca.firstname, com.name AS company, ocu.label AS occupation, ind.label AS industry, levenshtein("takahashi", LOWER(ca.lastname)) AS lastname_lev, levenshtein("hiroshi ", LOWER(ca.firstname)) AS firstname_lev , 100-(levenshtein("takahashihiroshi ", LOWER(CONCAT(ca.lastname, ca.firstname)))*100/LENGTH(CONCAT(ca.lastname, ca.firstname))) AS ratio  FROM sl_candidate AS ca  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile AS cap ON (cap.candidatefk = ca.sl_candidatepk) LEFT JOIN sl_occupation AS ocu ON (ocu.sl_occupationpk = cap.occupationfk) LEFT JOIN sl_industry AS ind ON (ind.sl_industrypk = cap.industryfk) LEFT JOIN sl_company AS com ON (com.sl_companypk = cap.companyfk) LEFT JOIN sl_contact AS cont ON (cont.itemfk = ca.sl_candidatepk) WHERE  ( (ca.lastname LIKE "takahashi%" AND levenshtein("hiroshi ", LOWER(ca.firstname)) < 3)  OR (ca.lastname LIKE "%takahashi" AND levenshtein("hiroshi ", LOWER(ca.firstname)) < 3) ) ORDER BY ratio DESC, lastname_lev ASC, ca.firstname ASC LIMIT 100 OFFSET 0

SELECT  levenshtein("inomata", TRIM(LOWER(scan.lastname))) AS lastname_lev ,  levenshtein("inomata", TRIM(LOWER(scan.firstname))) AS firstname_lev ,  100-(levenshtein("inomata", LOWER(scan.lastname))*100/LENGTH(scan.lastname)) AS ratio ,  100-(levenshtein("inomata", LOWER(scan.firstname))*100/LENGTH(scan.firstname)) AS ratio_rev ,  IF(scom.name LIKE "dole", 3, IF(scom.name LIKE "dole%", 2, 1)) as match_order , scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-07 11:44:01") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk)))  WHERE 1  AND ( scan.lastname LIKE "%inomata%" OR  scan.firstname LIKE "%inomata%" )   AND  scom.name LIKE "%dole%"   AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY  IF(MAX(ratio) >= MAX(ratio_rev), ratio, ratio_rev) DESC , lastname desc, firstname desc, PK desc  LIMIT  0 ,25

          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,

          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "% ECU %"  and even.content  LIKE  "% ADAS %" )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY TRIM(scan.lastname) ASC, TRIM(scan.firstname) ASC  LIMIT  0 ,25

SELECT  levenshtein("yutaka", TRIM(LOWER(scan.lastname))) AS lastname_lev ,  levenshtein("yutaka", TRIM(LOWER(scan.firstname))) AS firstname_lev ,  100-(levenshtein("yutaka", LOWER(scan.lastname))*100/LENGTH(scan.lastname)) AS ratio ,  100-(levenshtein("yutaka", LOWER(scan.firstname))*100/LENGTH(scan.firstname)) AS ratio_rev , scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-08 17:40:05") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk)))  WHERE 1  AND ( scan.lastname LIKE "%yutaka%" OR  scan.firstname LIKE "%yutaka%" )   AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY  IF(MAX(ratio) >= MAX(ratio_rev), ratio, ratio_rev) DESC , lastname desc, firstname desc, PK desc  LIMIT  0 ,25

SELECT min(pl2.sl_position_linkpk) as min_date_position, pl.sl_position_linkpk, pl.created_by as pl_created_by ,m.*, min(m2.sl_meetingpk) as min_date, pl.status as pl_status, pl.active as pl_active, slc._sys_status as candidate_status
        ,pl.date_completed , pl.date_created as ccm_create_date
        FROM sl_meeting m
        INNER JOIN sl_meeting m2 ON m2.candidatefk = m.candidatefk
        INNER JOIN sl_position_link pl ON pl.candidatefk = m.candidatefk
        INNER JOIN sl_candidate slc on slc.sl_candidatepk = m.candidatefk AND slc._sys_status = 0
        INNER JOIN sl_position_link pl2 ON pl2.candidatefk = pl.candidatefk
        WHERE pl.date_completed >= "2016-12-01"
        AND pl.date_completed <= "2017-02-09"
        AND pl.status = 51
        AND pl.active = 0
        AND pl2.status = 51
        AND pl2.active = 0
        AND slc._sys_status = 0
         AND m.meeting_done = 1 
        group by pl.candidatefk, pl.positionfk
        order by m.candidatefk

          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-09 14:03:30") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "% RPA %"  and scan.locationfk  IN  (1) )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY TRIM(scan.lastname) ASC, TRIM(scan.firstname) ASC  LIMIT  0 ,25

SELECT ca.sl_candidatepk, ca.lastname, ca.firstname, com.name AS company, ocu.label AS occupation, ind.label AS industry, levenshtein("takahashi", LOWER(ca.lastname)) AS lastname_lev, levenshtein("naotaka", LOWER(ca.firstname)) AS firstname_lev , 100-(levenshtein("takahashinaotaka", LOWER(CONCAT(ca.lastname, ca.firstname)))*100/LENGTH(CONCAT(ca.lastname, ca.firstname))) AS ratio  FROM sl_candidate AS ca  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile AS cap ON (cap.candidatefk = ca.sl_candidatepk) LEFT JOIN sl_occupation AS ocu ON (ocu.sl_occupationpk = cap.occupationfk) LEFT JOIN sl_industry AS ind ON (ind.sl_industrypk = cap.industryfk) LEFT JOIN sl_company AS com ON (com.sl_companypk = cap.companyfk) LEFT JOIN sl_contact AS cont ON (cont.itemfk = ca.sl_candidatepk) WHERE  ( (ca.lastname LIKE "takahashi%" AND levenshtein("naotaka", LOWER(ca.firstname)) < 3)  OR (ca.lastname LIKE "%takahashi" AND levenshtein("naotaka", LOWER(ca.firstname)) < 3) ) ORDER BY ratio DESC, lastname_lev ASC, ca.firstname ASC LIMIT 100 OFFSET 0

          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,

SELECT scpr.*, scrs.*, scan.*,
        scan.date_created as date_added,
        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,
        slog.loginpk as creatorfk, CONCAT(slog.firstname, " ", slog.lastname) as creator, slog.pseudo as creator_short,
        sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
        scom.name as company_name, scom.is_client as cp_client, scom.sl_companypk, scom.sl_companypk as companyfk,
        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,
        IF(sind2.label IS NOT NULL, sind2.label, IF(socc2.label IS NOT NULL, socc2.label,  satt.attributefk)) as attribute_label
         FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_attribute as satt ON ((satt.`type` IN ("candi_lang","candi_indus","candi_occu") AND itemfk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_language as slan ON ((slan.sl_languagepk = scan.languagefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_location as sloc ON ((sloc.sl_locationpk = scan.locationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_nationality as snat ON ((snat.sl_nationalitypk = scan.nationalityfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_indus" AND sind2.sl_industrypk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_occu" AND socc2.sl_occupationpk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON ((slog.loginpk = scan.created_by))  LEFT JOIN sl_company_rss as scrs ON ((scrs.companyfk = scom.sl_companypk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  WHERE 1  AND scan.sl_candidatepk = 311432 AND COALESCE(sind.sl_industrypk, 0) <> 126

SELECT ca.sl_candidatepk, ca.lastname, ca.firstname, com.name AS company, ocu.label AS occupation, ind.label AS industry, levenshtein("sato", LOWER(ca.lastname)) AS lastname_lev, levenshtein("junko", LOWER(ca.firstname)) AS firstname_lev , 100-(levenshtein("satojunko", LOWER(CONCAT(ca.lastname, ca.firstname)))*100/LENGTH(CONCAT(ca.lastname, ca.firstname))) AS ratio  FROM sl_candidate AS ca  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile AS cap ON (cap.candidatefk = ca.sl_candidatepk) LEFT JOIN sl_occupation AS ocu ON (ocu.sl_occupationpk = cap.occupationfk) LEFT JOIN sl_industry AS ind ON (ind.sl_industrypk = cap.industryfk) LEFT JOIN sl_company AS com ON (com.sl_companypk = cap.companyfk) LEFT JOIN sl_contact AS cont ON (cont.itemfk = ca.sl_candidatepk) WHERE  ( (ca.lastname LIKE "sato%" AND levenshtein("junko", LOWER(ca.firstname)) < 3)  OR (ca.lastname LIKE "%sato" AND levenshtein("junko", LOWER(ca.firstname)) < 3) ) ORDER BY ratio DESC, lastname_lev ASC, ca.firstname ASC LIMIT 100 OFFSET 0

          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-13 10:17:24") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk)))  WHERE 1  AND ( scan.lastname LIKE "takeshi%" OR  scan.firstname LIKE "takeshi%" )   AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY  IF(MAX(ratio) >= MAX(ratio_rev), ratio, ratio_rev) DESC , lastname desc, firstname desc, PK desc  LIMIT  0 ,25

        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,

        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,

         FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_attribute as satt ON ((satt.`type` IN ("candi_lang","candi_indus","candi_occu") AND itemfk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_language as slan ON ((slan.sl_languagepk = scan.languagefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_location as sloc ON ((sloc.sl_locationpk = scan.locationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_nationality as snat ON ((snat.sl_nationalitypk = scan.nationalityfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_indus" AND sind2.sl_industrypk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_occu" AND socc2.sl_occupationpk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON ((slog.loginpk = scan.created_by))  LEFT JOIN sl_company_rss as scrs ON ((scrs.companyfk = scom.sl_companypk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  WHERE 1  AND scan.sl_candidatepk = 349436 AND COALESCE(sind.sl_industrypk, 0) <> 126

          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,

          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,

SELECT fold.*, count(fite.folder_itempk) as nb_item, slog.pseudo,
      IF(lower(fold.label) = "pr", 1, 0) as str_equal,
      IF(lower(fold.label) LIKE "pr%", 1, 0) as str_start 
      FROM folder as fold
      INNER JOIN shared_login as slog ON (slog.loginpk = fold.ownerloginfk)
      LEFT JOIN folder_item as fite ON (fite.parentfolderfk = fold.folderpk)
      WHERE 1  AND  lower(fold.label) LIKE "%pr%" GROUP BY fold.folderpk
                  ORDER BY str_equal DESC, str_start DESC, fold.label, folderpk

SELECT scpr.*, scrs.*, scan.*,
        scan.date_created as date_added,
        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,
        slog.loginpk as creatorfk, CONCAT(slog.firstname, " ", slog.lastname) as creator, slog.pseudo as creator_short,
        sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
        scom.name as company_name, scom.is_client as cp_client, scom.sl_companypk, scom.sl_companypk as companyfk,
        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,
        IF(sind2.label IS NOT NULL, sind2.label, IF(socc2.label IS NOT NULL, socc2.label,  satt.attributefk)) as attribute_label
         FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_attribute as satt ON ((satt.`type` IN ("candi_lang","candi_indus","candi_occu") AND itemfk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_language as slan ON ((slan.sl_languagepk = scan.languagefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_location as sloc ON ((sloc.sl_locationpk = scan.locationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_nationality as snat ON ((snat.sl_nationalitypk = scan.nationalityfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_indus" AND sind2.sl_industrypk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_occu" AND socc2.sl_occupationpk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON ((slog.loginpk = scan.created_by))  LEFT JOIN sl_company_rss as scrs ON ((scrs.companyfk = scom.sl_companypk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  WHERE 1  AND scan.sl_candidatepk = 315129 AND COALESCE(sind.sl_industrypk, 0) <> 126

          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-15 11:28:32") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin , scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-15 11:29:22") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "% BPR %"  and scan.locationfk  IN  (1)  and (  (sind.sl_industrypk  IN  (120,503) OR sind.parentfk  IN  (120,503))  ) )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY full_salary asc  LIMIT  0 ,25

SELECT scpr.*, scrs.*, scan.*,
        scan.date_created as date_added,
        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,
        slog.loginpk as creatorfk, CONCAT(slog.firstname, " ", slog.lastname) as creator, slog.pseudo as creator_short,
        sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
        scom.name as company_name, scom.is_client as cp_client, scom.sl_companypk, scom.sl_companypk as companyfk,
        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,
        IF(sind2.label IS NOT NULL, sind2.label, IF(socc2.label IS NOT NULL, socc2.label,  satt.attributefk)) as attribute_label
         FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_attribute as satt ON ((satt.`type` IN ("candi_lang","candi_indus","candi_occu") AND itemfk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_language as slan ON ((slan.sl_languagepk = scan.languagefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_location as sloc ON ((sloc.sl_locationpk = scan.locationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_nationality as snat ON ((snat.sl_nationalitypk = scan.nationalityfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_indus" AND sind2.sl_industrypk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_occu" AND socc2.sl_occupationpk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON ((slog.loginpk = scan.created_by))  LEFT JOIN sl_company_rss as scrs ON ((scrs.companyfk = scom.sl_companypk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  WHERE 1  AND scan.sl_candidatepk = 404817 AND COALESCE(sind.sl_industrypk, 0) <> 126

        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,

        ,pl.date_completed , pl.date_created as ccm_create_date
        FROM sl_meeting m
        INNER JOIN sl_meeting m2 ON m2.candidatefk = m.candidatefk
        INNER JOIN sl_position_link pl ON pl.candidatefk = m.candidatefk
        INNER JOIN sl_candidate slc on slc.sl_candidatepk = m.candidatefk AND slc._sys_status = 0
        INNER JOIN sl_position_link pl2 ON pl2.candidatefk = pl.candidatefk
        WHERE pl.date_completed >= "2016-12-01"
        AND pl.date_completed <= "2017-02-17"
        AND pl.status = 51
        AND pl.active = 0
        AND pl2.status = 51
        AND pl2.active = 0
        AND slc._sys_status = 0
         AND m.meeting_done = 1 
        group by pl.candidatefk, pl.positionfk
        order by m.candidatefk

          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,

SELECT scpr.*, scrs.*, scan.*,
        scan.date_created as date_added,
        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,
        slog.loginpk as creatorfk, CONCAT(slog.firstname, " ", slog.lastname) as creator, slog.pseudo as creator_short,
        sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
        scom.name as company_name, scom.is_client as cp_client, scom.sl_companypk, scom.sl_companypk as companyfk,
        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,
        IF(sind2.label IS NOT NULL, sind2.label, IF(socc2.label IS NOT NULL, socc2.label,  satt.attributefk)) as attribute_label
         FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_attribute as satt ON ((satt.`type` IN ("candi_lang","candi_indus","candi_occu") AND itemfk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_language as slan ON ((slan.sl_languagepk = scan.languagefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_location as sloc ON ((sloc.sl_locationpk = scan.locationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_nationality as snat ON ((snat.sl_nationalitypk = scan.nationalityfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_indus" AND sind2.sl_industrypk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_occu" AND socc2.sl_occupationpk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON ((slog.loginpk = scan.created_by))  LEFT JOIN sl_company_rss as scrs ON ((scrs.companyfk = scom.sl_companypk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  WHERE 1  AND scan.sl_candidatepk = 154310

          FROM sl_company as scom

          WHERE  LENGTH(scom.name) > 1

        scom.name as company_name, scom.is_client as cp_client, scom.sl_companypk, scom.sl_companypk as companyfk,
        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,
        IF(sind2.label IS NOT NULL, sind2.label, IF(socc2.label IS NOT NULL, socc2.label,  satt.attributefk)) as attribute_label
         FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_attribute as satt ON ((satt.`type` IN ("candi_lang","candi_indus","candi_occu") AND itemfk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_language as slan ON ((slan.sl_languagepk = scan.languagefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_location as sloc ON ((sloc.sl_locationpk = scan.locationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_nationality as snat ON ((snat.sl_nationalitypk = scan.nationalityfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_indus" AND sind2.sl_industrypk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_occu" AND socc2.sl_occupationpk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON ((slog.loginpk = scan.created_by))  LEFT JOIN sl_company_rss as scrs ON ((scrs.companyfk = scom.sl_companypk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  WHERE 1  AND scan.sl_candidatepk = 417726 AND COALESCE(sind.sl_industrypk, 0) <> 126

          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-18 16:01:29") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin , scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-20 15:16:33") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON ((even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type <> "character" ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "%digital marketing%" )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) AND COALESCE(sind.sl_industrypk, 0) <> 126 GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY TRIM(scan.lastname) ASC, TRIM(scan.firstname) ASC  LIMIT  250 ,25

        scan.date_created as date_added,
        slog.firstname as cons_firstname, slog.lastname as cons_lastname,
        slog.loginpk as creatorfk, CONCAT(slog.firstname, " ", slog.lastname) as creator, slog.pseudo as creator_short,
        sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
        scom.name as company_name, scom.is_client as cp_client, scom.sl_companypk, scom.sl_companypk as companyfk,
        scrs.date_created as date_rss, sloc.location, slan.language, snat.nationality,
        (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title,

        satt.`type` as attribute_type,
        satt.attributefk as attribute_value,

         FROM `sl_candidate` as scan LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_attribute as satt ON ((satt.`type` IN ("candi_lang","candi_indus","candi_occu") AND itemfk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_language as slan ON ((slan.sl_languagepk = scan.languagefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_location as sloc ON ((sloc.sl_locationpk = scan.locationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_nationality as snat ON ((snat.sl_nationalitypk = scan.nationalityfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_indus" AND sind2.sl_industrypk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc2 ON ((satt.`type` = "candi_occu" AND socc2.sl_occupationpk = satt.attributefk))  LEFT JOIN shared_login as slog ON ((slog.loginpk = scan.created_by))  LEFT JOIN sl_company_rss as scrs ON ((scrs.companyfk = scom.sl_companypk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  WHERE 1  AND scan.sl_candidatepk = 314754

          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-20 16:56:17") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( even.content  LIKE  "%demand%" )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY TRIM(scan.lastname) ASC, TRIM(scan.firstname) ASC  LIMIT  0 ,25
14sec - start: 2017-02-20 16:56:29 / end: 2017-02-20 16:56:43
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-21 08:43:19") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin , scan.*,
          scom.name as company_name, scom.sl_companypk, scom.is_client as cp_client,
          (scpr.salary + scpr.bonus) as full_salary, scpr.grade, scpr.title, scpr._has_doc, scpr._in_play,
          scpr._pos_status, scpr.department, sind.label as industry, socc.label as occupation,
          TIMESTAMPDIFF(YEAR, scan.date_birth, "2017-02-21 08:46:33") AS age,
          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk) ) AND ( elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_type = "candi" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  INNER JOIN event as even ON (( even.eventpk = elin.eventfk AND even.type NOT IN ('cp_hidden', 'cp_history') ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  LEFT JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  WHERE 1   and ( scpr.grade  >= "0"  and even.content  LIKE  "%8448%" )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) AND COALESCE(sind.sl_industrypk, 0) <> 126 GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY TRIM(scan.lastname) ASC, TRIM(scan.firstname) ASC  LIMIT  20 ,10

SELECT count(DISTINCT scan.sl_candidatepk) as nCount FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN document_link as dlin ON ((dlin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND dlin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND dlin.cp_type = "candi" AND dlin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  INNER JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  INNER JOIN document_file as dfil ON (( dfil.documentfk = dlin.documentfk ))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk)))  WHERE 1   and ( scpr.grade  >= "0"  and (  (sind.sl_industrypk  IN  (505) OR sind.parentfk  IN  (505))  )  and (  (socc.sl_occupationpk  IN  (147) OR socc.parentfk  IN  (147))  )  and dfil.original  REGEXP  "(control|climate|air condition)"  )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0)

          scan.sl_candidatepk as PK, count(elin.eventfk) as nb_note, MAX(elin.event_linkpk) as lastNote, IF(_sys_redirect > 0, _sys_redirect, scan.sl_candidatepk) as PK, 0 as _is_admin  FROM `sl_candidate` as scan INNER JOIN document_link as dlin ON ((dlin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk AND dlin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND dlin.cp_type = "candi" AND dlin.cp_action = "ppav" ))  LEFT JOIN sl_candidate_profile as scpr ON ((scpr.candidatefk = scan.sl_candidatepk))  INNER JOIN sl_occupation as socc ON ((socc.sl_occupationpk = scpr.occupationfk))  INNER JOIN document_file as dfil ON (( dfil.documentfk = dlin.documentfk ))  LEFT JOIN sl_company as scom ON ((scom.sl_companypk = scpr.companyfk))  LEFT JOIN sl_industry as sind ON ((sind.sl_industrypk = scpr.industryfk))  LEFT JOIN event_link as elin ON (((elin.cp_uid = "555-001" AND elin.cp_action = "ppav" AND elin.cp_type="candi" AND elin.cp_pk = scan.sl_candidatepk)))  WHERE 1   and ( scpr.grade  >= "0"  and (  (sind.sl_industrypk  IN  (505) OR sind.parentfk  IN  (505))  )  and (  (socc.sl_occupationpk  IN  (147) OR socc.parentfk  IN  (147))  )  and dfil.original  REGEXP  "(control|climate|air condition)"  )  AND (_sys_status = 0 OR _sys_redirect > 0) GROUP BY scan.sl_candidatepk  ORDER BY TRIM(scan.lastname) ASC, TRIM(scan.firstname) ASC  LIMIT  0 ,25
